	* jm-glibc-io.m4: New file.

1998-05-19  Jim Meyering  <meyering@ascend.com>

	* jm-macros.m4: Add jm_FUNC_LCHOWN.
	* lchown.m4: New file.

	* Makefile.am.in: New file.
	* Makefile.am (Makefile.am): Depend on Makefile.am.in.

